The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Gambhir stars in victory
                                                                                                                       7                                      Gambhir stars in victory
                      
	Mohali: Gautam Gambhir played a captains knock as Delhi Daredevils started their campaign on a winning note beating Kings XI Punjab by five wickets in the third match of the Indian Premier League here on Saturday.         
	Chasing a scored 143, the Daredevils were off to a disastrous start losing two wickets in the second over when Sreesanth removed Virender Sehwag and TM Dilshan.         
	Then it was another dangerman AB de Villiers who was out in the eighth over. However Gambhir continued playing his shots at the other end.         
	(PTI)                                                                                                                     
